title: Unreal Helmet
longDescription: We all know gibs are messy. Post-match cleanup costs continue to rise year-over-year. With the new Unreal Helmet save yourself from the mess of a match with this full eye protection and helmet. In normal play it is just a helmet. As soon as you tie or take the lead in any game, the gold Unreal Tournament symbol appears on your helmet and your goggles glow gold.
